� General Information
This module provides data for CAN output. As in the different vehicle platforms of Volkswagen Group some
of the signals in CAN database are equal and other differ in physical meaning there are sections to de?ne
adaptation of platform speci?c and and common signals. Common signals may have to be switched.
To be able to reuse CAN specs. in all projects for VW Group the variables de?ned in this module should be the
same for every project speci?c version.
Variables of torque structure are adapted to generic CAN interface.
